topic.title: SPI Slave Timing

body.p: This section describes the SPI slave timing.
The following table is based on a load of 30 pF on each output with a GPIO output drive strength of 3.

entry.p: Chip select falling to CLK set up time1
CLK to chip select rising hold time1
CLK to MOSI data hold time1
CLK to MOSI data set up time1
CLK to MISO data out time1

li.p: Includes all master outputs: SPI-S_CSn, SPI-S_CLK, and SPI-S_MOSI.
